➜安倍宣布辞职，对日本有何影响？继任者将面临哪些问题？
http://www.sohu.com/a/415459699_115376	6649
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
